        <hl1>Word's Not Perfect</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>One letter about the WordPerfect column (Sept. 28) said, ''Allowing Microsoft to offer bundled software to PC system vendors is the real Microsoft monopoly threat.'' Really? If you don't care for the software that Microsoft offers you free, just uninstall it. I think that most consumers appreciate getting Microsoft Word and other software at no charge -- I know that I do.</p>
        <p>STANLEY J. SCHAFFER  Scarsdale, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
